{
  "stem": "26983.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we heard rumors that Jews are sent to this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had an uncle in Brunn, and he went to this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I also remember that some of our teachers who came from Brunn had to go to Brunn, so that they could go with the transport to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mahrisch Ostrau came somehow later to be sent off to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of the reasons was that in Mahrisch Ostrau was-- the head of the Jewish community was Salo Kramer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Kramer action, aktion, was to confiscate the Jewish flats which were left after the deportation, and to put it in order, and to give it over to the German.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was one of his jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And therefore, the German kept him even later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Even when all Jews were evacuated to Theresienstadt, he and a few others were left so he could-- to care for this-- for this thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To take care of-- to take over all these flats.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we heard from the Jewish community that since the Jews in Mahrisch Ostrau were the first to suffer-- their husbands were sent to Nisko in '39-- the Gestapo promised them they will be the last to be sent to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they didn't care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They knew what will happen anyhow in the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the fact is, we were sent to Theresienstadt only in autumn '42.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were four transport to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it went according-- numbers-- Just a second.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before that, was the idea to send all the Jews of Czechoslovakia to Theresienstadt together in one ghetto?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew only that there are transported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, we know there was some transport that went straight to Riga.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A couple of thousands of Jews--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Riga and-- or to other places and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
